{"tid":715451,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"Cocina 3 Tapas 食評","createTime":"2018-06-24T13:23:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T19:24:58.000Z","uid":175988,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"103fe59799e804d42a1982e0141c435908491d09","tid":715451,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T13:23:05.000Z","msg":"<strong>Cocina 3 Tapas Restaurant &amp; Bar @ 奧海城</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/a6LukGN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fa6LukGN.jpg&h=39b6f673&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ShUCPa5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FShUCPa5.jpg&h=41ce14b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Seafood Risotto / Churros</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAfternoon tea 無paella惟有食risotto，估唔到都幾好，米粒做到al dente，蕃茄醬base濃度夠，酸中帶微甜，如果更加creamy就好<br />\n<br />\n大蝦有炭燒香味，都算厚肉<br />\n<br />\nChurros外酥脆，入面軟中帶煙韌，肉桂粉份量適中，唔點朱古力醬已經夠味<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n海鮮全部雪藏貨，海水鹹鮮味明顯欠奉，但肉質唔會rubbery或者霉，$60左右一個大蝦risotto嚟講都算係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>結論: 咁嘅價位屬高質之選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<br />\nBtw大家有冇抵屌嘅Spanish restaurant推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9701cb434f4c2a0deea1ba191833e63d952e2e05","tid":715451,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T13:58:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a986b3417c4ca76dc27843ac5ffbeaa250dc079","tid":715451,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T10:54:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa58434c95fc2b20e822634ab64120a8bf7432cd","tid":715451,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T16:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e7ad470d421fbf68541554fa299111b9761d59","tid":715451,"uid":20138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T19:24:58.000Z","msg":"依間食過唔錯"}]}